      "text": "INPUT (set once)\n  story_state: StoryState\n  t_start: float\n\nFROM generate_text / retry_text\n  raw_text: str\n  narrative: str\n  choices_raw: list[str]\n\nFROM safety_check\n  safety: SafetyResult\n  safety_retry_count: int\n\nFROM generate_media\n  narration_audio_bytes: bytes\n  main_image_bytes: bytes\n  choice_audio_bytes: list[bytes]\n  choice_image_bytes: list[bytes]\n\nFROM assemble\n  scene_output: SceneOutput\n\n\u2500\u2500 Merge semantics \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\nEach node returns only the\nkeys it mutates. LangGraph\nshallow-merges into full state.",
